        "@value": "https://nac-cna.ca/en/event/41382"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Glenn Gould Piano Recital | Cécile Desrosiers and Thomas Nicholson |  Wed, May 13, 2026, 1:00 pm | Southam Hall Mezzanine Foyer"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/41382/cd_318_-_photo_2__large.jpg"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "In celebration of Glenn Gould, his long-lasting musical legacy, and his beloved CD 318 Steinway piano, this salon-style concert features Cécile Desrosiers and Thomas Nicholson playing the music of Bach, Handel, Haydn, Jacquet de La Guerre, Debussy, and more. The music selections reflect some of the composers Gould was most fond of including most notably Bach.\n\nDeeply cherished by Gould, CD 318 has lived at the NAC as both an artefact and living instrument since its transfer from Library and Archives..."
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns/fb#admins": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "728780803"
      }
