    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Cranium Arts Project is excited to announce the Cranium Conference and Showcase 2026. \n\nThe music event will connect active industry professionals with musicians, artists and people making moves in the arts and entertainment business. The weekend will feature networking sessions, information panels with music professionals, masterclasses, and a showcase featuring some great emerging talent.\n\nSchedule: Friday, May 8, 2026 \n\n5:15 – 6:25 pm: Artist Branding and Identity\n\nAtelier Shenkman Smith – FREE, registration required\nThis workshop explores artist branding and identity. Emerging artists will have the..."
      }
    ],
